  "text": "The purpose of the outlier distribution p 0 (x nd ) is to explain the outlier cells in the dataset, completely removing their effect in the optimization of the parameters of clean component p θ . For categorical features, we propose using the uniform distribution p 0 (x nd ) = C d −1 . Such a uniform distribution assumption has been used in multiple object modelling [CITATION_1] as a way to factor in pixel occlusion.",
